freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: I have an underlying polymyaliga rheumatica for which I am taking ever decreasing doses of Prednisone.  I was down to 2mg and had a sudden flare-up of pain in my back, hips and thighs.  I increased the dosage to 4mg and they have subsided.
